<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card p-4">
    <h1 class="float-left">About US</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "tiger.jpg", alt: 'Profile Image', width: '100%' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |s| %>
            <div class="container mt-3 p-0">
              <h4><%= s.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                role="progressbar"
                aria-valuenow="<%= s.percent_utilized %>"
                aria-valuemax="100"
                style="width: <%= s.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolores quos cum enim asperiores. Velit vitae nulla delectus sed laborum provident quas autem ad doloribus mollitia. Distinctio, officia optio, ipsam quaerat tempora quas saepe quibusdam accusamus aliquam magnam aperiam atque. Soluta.</p>
        <p>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              Job 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              Job 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block mt-1 p-3">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
